notification.contentToBeAnonymized: Okuqukethwe kwakho kuzocashwa ngokungaziwa ezinsukwini eziyi-7 ngenxa
notification.communityContentToBeAnonymized: Yonke imininingwane yakho kulo mphakathi izocashwa ngokungaziwa futhi igcinwe ezinsukwini eziyi-7, ngemva kwalokho ngeke ukwazi ukuyisusa noma uyishintshe. Bheka okuqukethwe kwakho ngezansi.
notification.groupContentToBeAnonymized: Yonke imininingwane yakho kuleli qembu izocashwa ngokungaziwa futhi igcinwe ezinsukwini eziyi-7, ngemva kwalokho ngeke ukwazi ukuyisusa noma uyishintshe. Bheka okuqukethwe kwakho ngezansi.

email.possibleFraudFooter: Chofoza isixhumanisi somphakathi esingezansi, ngena njengomphathi bese ukhetha Ukuphathwa kobugebengu kumenyu.
email.possibleFraudSubHeader: Inani lezenzo ezingase zibe ubugebengu ezinamathuba angama-75% okuba ubugebengu
email.possibleFraudInformation: Uhlelo lwethu oluzenzakalelayo luthole umsebenzi ongase ube ubugebengu. Ungabheka ngokucophelela nge-Community admin interface. Eminye yale misebenzi ingase ibe nezizathu ezingekho emthethweni ngakho qaphela ukuphenya ngokucophelela ngaphambi kokususa okuqukethwe.
email.automaticToxicityDetection: Lokuqukethwe kubekwe uphawu ngokuzenzakalelayo njengokunobuthi kusetshenziswa ama-algorithms e-AI akala ubuthi bokuqukethwe. Ungasusa okuqukethwe uma kudingeka.
email.automaticToxicityDetectionVision: I-algorithm ye-AI ngokuzenzakalelayo ibeke uphawu lwezithombe ezihambisana nalokuqukethwe. Leli algorithm lihlola izithombe zokungenzeka kwabantu abadala, udlame, ezokwelapha, nezithombe ezinobulili. Ungasusa okuqukethwe uma kudingeka.
email.automaticToxicityDetectionDisclaimer: Ngezinye izikhathi i-algorithm ye-AI ibala amaphuzu angalungile, kulokhu ungakhathazeki, awudingi ukuthatha noma yisiphi isinyathelo esingeziwe futhi ungaziba le imeyili.
email.user_invite_2: Chofoza kusixhumanisi noma unamathisele kubha yekheli lesiphequluli ukwamukela isimemo
email.reset_password_2: Uma ungakucelanga lokhu, sicela uzibe le imeyili.
email.reset_password_3: Iphasiwedi yakho ngeke ishintshe kuze kube uyafinyelela isixhumanisi esingenhla bese udala entsha.
